Upload file:
hadoop fs -put - <input file>
    Example: hadoop fs -put - /gutenberg/in/1342.txt

Run file:
jar <local jar file> <Main class> <remote in dir> <remote out dir>
    Example: jar popular.jar dk.itu.sad2.Popular /gutenberg/in/ /gutenberg/out/

Remove file:
hadoop dfs -rmr <Remote file>
    Example: hadoop dfs -rmr /gutenberg/out/